        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped vegetables</strong> to one side of the baking tray (use<strong> baking paper</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Drizzle over a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs </strong>to the other side</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1612276890649-x200.jpg",
