    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>harissa paste</strong> and <strong>honey</strong> in a bowl and stir to combine – this is your <strong>honey harissa marinade</strong></p><p>Coat the <strong>chicken thighs </strong>in<strong> half </strong>the<strong> marinade </strong>and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 15 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
