    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>While the chicken is in the oven, drain and rinse the <strong>chickpeas</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> drained chickpeas</strong>,<strong> chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> ras el hanout </strong>in a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up until the chickpeas are fully coated – these are your <strong>spiced chickpeas</strong></p>",
